    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "1. Reference is made to Spot Report T-X from this Headquarters",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "dated 30 June 1950, making reference to an unidentified flying object",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "sighted on 29 June 1950 at Phoenix, Arizona.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "2. An interview with 1st Lt. JOHN D. FINK, AO-23052, 93rd",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "Fighter Squadron, Kirtland AFB reveals that on 29 June 1950 at approximately 1840 hours Lt. FINK sighted this object. Lt. [unclear] climbed to",
      "status": "correction_required"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "17,000 while flying an F-86 aircraft and observed that the object was",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "a bright balloon with instruments attached and was floating at an",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "altitude of 50,000 feet.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "3. Lt. FINK described the speed of the balloon as being very",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "slow and further described the balloon as being an \"inverted [unclear]",
      "status": "correction_required"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "drop\".",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "4. Inasmuch as the previously unidentified object has been",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "positively identified as a balloon, further investigation will not",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "be conducted in this incident.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
